# AI Horse Racing Predictor System

## Overview
Advanced machine learning system for horse racing predictions using ensemble models and real-time data analysis.

## Features
- Real-time race card analysis
- Machine learning predictions
- Value bet detection
- Performance tracking
- Betting simulation

## Installation
1. Run `setup_system.bat`
2. Run `start_server.bat`
3. Open http://localhost:5000

## Directory Structure
- `data/raw/`: Raw data collection
- `data/processed/`: Processed datasets
- `models/`: ML models and experiments
- `logs/`: System logs

## Usage
1. Initialize AI system
2. Load/generate race data
3. View predictions
4. Run simulations

